title: Wylie And The Wild West - Bucking Horse Moon
description:
These songs are song with all the energy that Wylie imparts to his music. The album, Bucking Horse Moon, is filled with yodels, songs about open space and the western lifestyle, cowboy culture, and always horses. These 14 new songs were recorded at the world renown Cash Cabin Studios with John Carter Cash (Johnny\&#039;s son) producing. The album is an even mixture of new originals and unique covers and is just plain \&#039;dynamite\&#039; to listen to.
